Phishing Email Analysis - Task 2
Drata Security System Account Inactivity Scam Analysis
Elevate Labs Cybersecurity Internship
Task 2: Analyze a Phishing Email Sample
Date: October 22, 2025
Analyst: Cybersecurity Intern

Project Overview
This repository contains a comprehensive analysis of a real phishing email impersonating the Drata Security System. The email uses an account inactivity scam technique to trick recipients into providing credentials on a fake login page. This analysis was completed as part of the Elevate Labs Cybersecurity Internship Task 2.

Objective
Identify phishing characteristics in a suspicious email sample and document findings in a detailed security report, demonstrating practical skills in:

Email threat detection and analysis

Social engineering recognition

Phishing indicator identification

Incident response procedures

Security documentation and reporting
